tics: availability taxonomy, task-clustered frame (55 rows / 50 candidate units / 37 tasks), decision curves, missingness manifest, and a materialization receipt binding 163 named predecessor blobs. All five V2 artifacts rebuild exactly.\n- Role-view leakage controls validate: 8 views, 52 fields, all known-bad fixtures rejected.\n\n## Registered status (unchanged)\ndesign_preflight: supported. retained_evidence_recovery: blocked. independent_ground_truth: blocked. cohort_acquisition: not_authorized. k=0, N=37, u=13 unchanged. External spend $0.00; zero provider/model calls, containers, executions, GPU allocations, human contacts, or adjudications.\n\n## Boundary\nA reproducing design and a frozen selector are not semantic ground truth, prevalence, detector efficacy, transfer, or a scientific claim. GROUND-TRUTH-1 remains blocked on separately authorized funding, conflict-screened humans, data handling, and execution.\n\n## Provenance\nAdditions-only completed-evidence commit under the iter240 authorization; exact-tree successor seal registered in mission/seal_registry.json (27 blobs). Local CI closure clean (292/292); sealed-head CI green on Python 3.11 and 3.12.","created_at":"2026-07-19T23:24:42Z","updated_at":"2026-07-19T23:30:25Z","closed_at":"2026-07-19T23:30:24Z","merged_at":"2026-07-19T23:30:24Z","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/pulls/88/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/pulls/88/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/issues/88/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/statuses/f954696c935ad0b733dcd613b553e1799a7b3810","head":{"label":"manfromnowhere143:agent/iter240-ground-truth-admission-design","